{"tid":1724820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]   唔好再forward 依一段不割蓆宣言？","createTime":"2019-11-15T14:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T15:05:00.000Z","uid":56518,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1534c9b7af216dc733fae1d6658992b2d825f750","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"事先聲明，只係想警醒下大家，唔係割<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyCdAwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyCdAwW.png&h=1cb9a7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到今日facebook比依段宣言洗版，越諗越唔妥<br />\n<br />\n可能你地覺得&rdquo;哼我唔割!&rdquo;依一個訊息可以令你站在示威者的一方。<br />\n係，我認同。<br />\n<br />\n但依段文字最大問題係，你話比大家知<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你只係站在示威者的後方，而唔係同行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;本人&rdquo;</span></span>絕不埋怨<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&rdquo;示威者&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n我者 vs 他者之隔<br />\n<br />\n喂，大哥呀，我地理應係同一陣線，半年喇、死左人喇，你仲係講到唔撚關你事咁<br />\n<br />\n依個唔係立場的問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">依個係意識的問題</span><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;你&rdquo;堵路<br />\n&ldquo;你&rdquo;塞鐵<br />\n<br />\n點解唔撚係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;我地&rdquo;堵路<br />\n&ldquo;我地&rdquo;塞鐵???!!</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個香港大家有份嫁屌你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85dff886574bd90d0471a4a708921d0509a02ae","tid":1724820,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4409e4d363385edf11108c322b2461eff2a34aa2","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"要forward就forward依個！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聲明：<br />\n就算現在生活有多不便，除非政府答應五大訴求，否則我們不會暫停及放棄不合作運動，甚至升級三罷，請香港政府死心。<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7d214b98f3dc0733e89cc4800f40eb55b6aa1666","tid":1724820,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:35:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e80f9be9974a38330b25569c182c47a26768f58","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c924e18d388b812cd52f76c22e2ed11791babb0","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab5a04f7405287e7bf18f25f3feee521db44dd81","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76466d632997dc9dc0e8a24e5ff3d6d6c75a1d2b","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:40:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28ae8f0bebea1a30b8e77e1ec377c6f9b68662d1","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"屌冇人推我自己推"},{"pid":"083fa605521d49efe5fcfa04c8118052228382ac","tid":1724820,"uid":275730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"我諗個聲明係想俾手足知,<br />\n香港市民沉默大多數並冇因為不合作運動而覺得唔應該做<br />\n反而係支持"},{"pid":"e16ce262a73634b771ca5c64eb46fe8600828417","tid":1724820,"uid":56518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"083fa605521d49efe5fcfa04c8118052228382ac","tid":1724820,"uid":275730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"我諗個聲明係想俾手足知,<br />\n香港市民沉默大多數並冇因為不合作運動而覺得唔應該做<br />\n反而係支持"},